name: Copilot
description: GitHub Copilot is an AI-powered code completion tool that provides suggestions and code snippets to developers as they write code. However, there are significant privacy concerns as it sends code snippets to an external server for processing, potentially exposing proprietary or sensitive code. Additionally, Copilot's training on public repositories raises questions about code ownership and the inclusion of potentially sensitive information in its suggestions.
